SASS Installation Steps:

1. Install Node Version Manager (nvm):
   curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash

2. Exit and reopen terminal to activate nvm

3. Install Node.js v20.16:
   nvm install 20.16

4. Verify Node.js installation:
   node -v  # Should show v20.16.x
   npm -v   # Should show version 10.x.x

5. Install SASS:
   npm install -g sass@3.7.4

6. Verify SASS installation:
   sass --version  # Should show 3.7.4
